text: Piotr Bujnarowski (born 4 July 1972) is a Polish rower. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Toruń
